  margin: 0;
  padding-bottom: 20px;
  font-size: 14px;
  list-style: none;
}
.timeline-widget .bto-timeline-item-label {
  position: absolute;
  top: -7.001px;
  width: calc(30% - 12px);
  text-align: right;
  color: #000;
}
.timeline-widget .bto-timeline .bto-timeline-item-label {
  position: absolute;
  top: -7.001px;

}

  height: calc(100% - 10px);

  left: 30%;

  position: absolute;

  height: 10px;
  background-color: #fff;

  border-color: #FF6C00;
  margin-left: -4px;
}

  left: calc(33% - 4px);
  width: calc(60% - 14px);
  text-align: left;

  top: -7.001px;
  margin: 0 0 0 18px;
  word-break: break-word;
  color: #000;

  height: 100%;

  z-index: 1000001;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  background-color: #fff;
  overflow-y: hidden;
}
@media (min-width: 740px) {
  .overlayWhite {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .overlayWhite .lds-ripple {
    display: inline-block;
    position: relative;
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
  }
  .overlayWhite .lds-ripple div {
    position: absolute;
    border: 4px solid #857e78;
    opacity: 1;
    border-radius: 50%;
    animation: lds-ripple 1s cubic-bezier(0, 0.2, 0.8, 1) infinite;
  }
  .overlayWhite .lds-ripple div:nth-child(2) {
    animation-delay: -0.5s;
  }
  @keyframes lds-ripple {
    0% {
      top: 36px;
      left: 36px;
      width: 0;
      height: 0;
      opacity: 1;
    }
    100% {
      top: 0px;
      left: 0px;
      width: 72px;
      height: 72px;
      opacity: 0;
    }
  }
}
